{"tid":2121654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"25歲女子涉藏雷射筆被控 月底屯門法院提堂","createTime":"2020-07-23T12:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T01:20:34.000Z","uid":133038,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4e6e092dc1c4075b3c9d3fad6d226b2d81cd910a","tid":2121654,"uid":133038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:31:39.000Z","msg":"上年8月11日晚上，警方接獲市民報案，指有示威者懷疑在屯門杯渡路一帶堵路。警方趕抵現場後隨即在附近一帶搜捕。期間，警方於屯盛街截停2男1女，該3名人士當時身懷多樣示威中常見的物品，並在當中一名25歲本地女子身上檢獲一支雷射筆。經初步調查，3名人士涉嫌「藏有攻擊性武器」被捕。該名25歲女子其後拒保候查。<br />\n警方經進一步調查及徵詢法律意見後，今日（23日）下午約12時45分在青山區再拘捕該名25歲女子，並控告該名女子一項「藏有攻擊性武器」罪，案件將於本月31日下午在屯門裁判法院提堂。<br />\n警方重申絕對不會容忍任何違法行為，不論政治背景或者政治訴求，只要有人觸犯法例，警方必定會果斷執法，全力調查搜證，將罪犯繩之於法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a28c502b59dfa85491047988a2a42f269bb3d3","tid":2121654,"uid":123774,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C1ayHTT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC1ayHTT.jpg&h=f7aeb45b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0dc6d8b75b5a3e6759d604c5f5ae0ee9114fe9b4","tid":2121654,"uid":133038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T13:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825e0f4b789bc08d3d50098ff4b2b25c5d69ad24","tid":2121654,"uid":39710,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T13:59:47.000Z","msg":"所有有關鐳射筆嘅案都係戇鳩"},{"pid":"ed32b3b8